            <div id="section_grey_line"></div>
            <p>Question: Which of the following is an event emitter?</p>

            <select name="valid" class="qa2" style="width:400px;height:40px;">
                <option data-value="qa2a">a) once</option>
                <option data-value="qa2b">b) process</option>
                <option data-value="qa2c">c) listeners</option>
                <option data-value="qa2d">d) on</option>
            </select>
            <br>
            <div id="section_grey_line"></div>
            <p>Question: Which method can be defined only once in a program?</p>

            <select name="method" class="qa3" style="width:400px;height:40px;">
                <option data-value="qa3a">a) main method</option>
                <option data-value="qa3b">b) finalize method</option>
                <option data-value="qa3c">c) static method</option>
                <option data-value="qa3d">d) private method</option>
            </select>
            <br>
            <div id="section_grey_line"></div>
            <p>Question: What is the method used to pause "data" events?</p>

            <select name="cars" class="qa4" style="width:400px;height:40px;">
                <option data-value="qa4a">a) s.pause();</option>
                <option data-value="qa4b">b) s.stop();</option>
                <option data-value="qa4c">c) s.halt();</option>
                <option data-value="qa4d">d) s.wait();</option>
            </select>
            <br>
            <div id="section_grey_line"></div>
